Orario:
1 marzo-31 maggio:
mercoledi' e giovedi' 9-13; venerdi', sabato, domenica e festivi 9-13 / 15-18;
1 giugno-31 agosto:
mercoledi' e giovedi' 9-13; venerdi', sabato, domenica e festivi 9-13 / 16-19;
1 settembre-31 ottobre:
mercoledi' e giovedi' 9-13; venerdi', sabato, domenica e festivi 9-13 / 15-18;
1 novembre-28 febbraio:
sabato e domenica 9-13 / 14-17.
Tutti i lunedi' e martedi' il parco e il museo sono chiusi al pubblico.

Opening times:
March 1st-May 31st:
Wednesday & Thursday 9am-1pm; Friday, Saturday, Sunday and holidays 9am-1pm / 3pm-6pm;
June 1st-August 31st:
Wednesday & Thursday 9am-1pm; Friday, Saturday, Sunday and holidays 9am-1pm / 4pm-7pm;
September 1st-October 31st:
Wednesday & Thursday 9am-1pm; Friday, Saturday, Sunday and holidays 9am-1pm / 3pm-6pm;
November 1st-February 28th: 
Saturday and Sunday 9am-1pm / 2pm-5pm.
On Mondays and on Tuesdays park and museums are closed.

Orario:
da novembre a febbraio: sabato e domenica ore 9-16.30;
marzo e ottobre: da mercoledi' a domenica ore 9-18; aprile: da mercoledi' a domenica ore 9-20;
maggio e settembre: da martedi' a domenica ore 9-20; da giugno a agosto: martedi'-domenica ore 8.30-21.

Opening times:
November thru' February: Saturdays and Sundays 9 am to 4.30 pm;
March and October: Wednesday thru' Sunday 9 am to 6 pm;
April: Wednesday thru' Sunday 9 am to 8 pm;
May and September: Tuesday thru' Sunday 9 am to 8 pm;
June thru' August: Tuesday thru' Sunday 8.30 am to 9 pm.
